# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

MOSAIC_IMAGES - Recipe for mosaicking SCUBA-2 images

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A simple PICARD recipe combine SCUBA-2 images taking into account the
exp_time NDF component.

All the input images should be of the same source. The recipe will
abort with an error if this is not the case.

For best results the images should be trimmed to remove noisy edges
using the PICARD recipe C<CROP_IMAGES>.

=head1 NOTES

None.

=head1 DISPLAY

No display is used by this recipe.

